The '''trans-system data storage library''' was an information repository located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Halowan]]. It contained, among other things, information on [[Star system/Legends|star systems]] throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

After evacuating [[Echo Base/Legends|Echo Base]] in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]], [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance to Restore the Republic]] historian [[Voren Na'al/Legends|Voren Na'al]] visited the library, where he compiled a good deal of information on the [[Hoth system/Legends|Hoth system]] and the geography of [[Hoth/Legends|Hoth]] for his records.<ref name="GG3">''[[Galaxy Guide 3: The Empire Strikes Back]]''</ref>

